title: Global Day of Coderetreat 2015 - Toronto, Canada
description:
Come to LoyaltyOne's downtown Toronto offices to join developers all around the world in a day-long, intensive practice event, focusing on the fundamentals of software development and design. 
Please register through Eventbrite (https://www.eventbrite.com/e/global-day-of-code-retreat-toronto-canada-tickets-19267087377).
